io.jeo.geom

Class GeometryAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.jeo.geom.GeometryAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeometryVisitor

    public class GeometryAdapter
extends Object
implements GeometryVisitor
    Adapter for GeometryVisitor.

    This base class does not descend by default. To cause it to decend either use the GeometryAdapter(boolean) constructor to enable descend for all objects, or override the individual methods.
